alerts.header: Westbound trains skip Elmont-UBS Arena, Queens Village, and Hollis
alerts.text:
MTA buses will accept LIRR tickets for travel from Queens Village and Hollis to Jamaica. View a map of your route options.

Elmont-UBS Arena riders should use Bellerose station instead.

Follow this link for information about transferring at the Jamaica Bus Terminal.

What's happening?

Accessibility improvements
alerts.human_duration: Weeknights, Nov 10 - 12, 17 - 19, 20 - 21, and 24 - 26, 10 PM to 3 AM

station_alternatives.text: Q2, Q36, or Q82 to Jamaica Bus Terminal, or Q110 to Parsons Blvd, for Q6 to Jamaica LIRR
